SEARCH
Module OOPCAMSFinalcodes
Package controllers

Class DatabaseSearchManager

java.lang.Object
controllers.DatabaseSearchManager
public class DatabaseSearchManager extends Object
The DatabaseSearchManager class provides methods for searching various databases within the system. It offers specialized search functionality for camps, students, staff, committee members, suggestions, enquiries, and mailboxes using different search criteria.
